      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It’s completely natural to feel overwhelmed by these challenging times, but it’s also good to remember that many people are feeling similarly. Yes, inflation and the cost of living continue to rise for a multitude of reasons including supply chain disruptions and increases in energy prices globally. While those in power play various roles in influencing these factors, there are also collective efforts at the governmental and societal levels to address these issues. It may not be lessening the challenge, but your concerns and further discussion on policy can be a constructive next step. Remember, seeking support from community groups, financial planning resources, or economic experts can also provide some guidance and relief during this period.",
